<plot>When you're frustrated with reality, your imagination can be the best place to escape to. But when a quiet teenage girl blurs the line between fantasy and real life, she sees that ruling your own world can be a lonely business, and that the things we want most are often the things that we can't have. This beautiful, visually imaginative short film looks at the small things in a big day of a young girl's life.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?064197</url></doc>
